item.title: 17923 Spoke Hollow Ct
item.dc:creator: sxv5304
item.content:encoded:
This exquisitely appointed and luxurious waterfront residence offers an exceptional living experience. Its pristine condition rivals that of a showcase home and evokes the aesthetics of a high-end magazine spread. Notably, it stands as the sole property on the market in Towne Lake featuring both a boathouse and a dock. Ideally situated within the secluded Waterway enclave of Towne Lake, this residence is one of only 15 homes within a private, gated cul-de-sac.
Enjoy the convenience of taking your family out on the water to bask in the island's sandy shores or dine and revel in entertainment at The Boardwalk. Once you've had your fill of adventure, securely moor your boat in your very own backyard, which features a personal boathouse with a private dock. The patio is an ideal space for hosting gatherings, watching TV, immersing yourself in music, or observing the local wildlife. You can even cast a line from your own backyard and enjoy some leisurely fishing. This property is complemented by a pool-ready lot with endless potential for design.
The discerning eye will notice the multitude of enhancements and amenities throughout the home. Each room has been thoughtfully customized to elevate the living experience. Furthermore, this home is move-in ready and boasts the benefits of low taxes, minimal maintenance, and cost-effective utility bills.
